                <h1>Understanding the Illinois Employee Background Fairness Act</h1>
                <p>The Illinois Employee Background Fairness Act aims to promote fairness in employment opportunities by regulating how employers use criminal background checks. It prohibits denials of employment based solely on criminal history unless it directly relates to the job. This ensures a fair chance for job seekers in Illinois, promoting rehabilitation and reducing discrimination.</p>
